name: bugfix
description: Focused bug fix flow
timeout_min: 45

# NUM | AGENT | CLI | GATE | PARALLEL_GROUP | TIMEOUT_MIN | PROMPT
0 | base     | - | auto | - | 5  | Preflight check: Run META/scripts/preflight-gate.sh --project . and report results in .handoff.md. If blockers exist, stop and list what needs to be fixed.
1 | debugger | - | auto | - | -  | Diagnose the root cause from .handoff.md. Update .handoff.md with findings.
2 | base     | - | auto | - | -  | Implement fix and add regression test. Update .handoff.md with changes.
3 | reviewer | - | gate | - | -  | Review fix for correctness and security. Update .handoff.md with findings.
4 | base     | - | auto | - | -  | Run META/prompts/definition-of-done-checklist.md. Note gaps in .handoff.md.
5 | base     | - | gate | - | -  | Final quality gate. Run META/scripts/quality-gate.sh --project . and report results in .handoff.md. If checks fail, fix what you can and re-run.
